    "bio": "Hi, I'm Darshan Patel — a professional photographer with a passion for storytelling. I specialize in the moments that matter most: housewarming ceremonies that mark new beginnings, birthday and farewell celebrations, baby showers filled with the joy of new life, and personal or professional photoshoots that truly showcase your personality.\n\nI bring state-of-the-art equipment, a creative eye, and a friendly, approachable presence to every session — so you can relax and be yourself while I capture the moments worth remembering forever.\n\nWith a quick 24–48 hour turnaround and personalized service tailored to your vision, my goal is simple: to make every memory last.",
